            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 mb-8 border border-light-border">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-laser-blue">User Status & Presence</h3>
                <p class="text-light-text-secondary mb-6">
                    Track user status (online/offline) and manage presence information across different topics/rooms.
